<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id=3D"FAQ:FrequentlyAskedQuestionsabouteZProducts-Editing.2">Editing</h=
3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id=3D"expander-302753298" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-302753298" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"af918576c0365dadd34b26056af46801" widt=
h=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span>
<span class=3D"expand-control-text">How does a Landing Page differ from a r=
egular page?</span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-$toggleId" class=3D"expand-content">
<p>A Landing Page is a special kind of a Content item. It is a page designe=
d to be the visitor's entry point into your website.</p>
<p>A Landing Page has a customizable layout with multiple zones where you c=
an place predefined blocks with dynamic content.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-1549072885" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-1549072885" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"af918576c0365dadd34b26056af46801" widt=
h=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span>
<span class=3D"expand-control-text">How do I create a Landing Page?</span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-$toggleId" class=3D"expand-content">
<p class=3D"confluence-link">You can create a new Landing Page in the Page =
mode by clicking <strong>Create</strong>. See&nbsp;<a href=3D"/display/USER=
/Creating+content+-+Landing+Page">Creating content - Landing Page</a> for m=
ore information.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-901461911" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-901461911" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"af918576c0365dadd34b26056af46801" widt=
h=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span>
<span class=3D"expand-control-text">What blocks can I add to a Landing Page=
?</span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-$toggleId" class=3D"expand-content">
<p>Here is the <a href=3D"/display/USER/Adding+blocks+to+Landing+Page">list=
 of predefined Landing Page blocks</a>.</p>
<p>You also have the possibility of <a href=3D"/pages/viewpage.action?pageI=
d=3D31430614">creating your own, custom blocks</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-111646790" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-111646790" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"af918576c0365dadd34b26056af46801" widt=
h=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span>
<span class=3D"expand-control-text">How can I make content appear on a page=
 at a predefined time?</span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-$toggleId" class=3D"expand-content">
<p>You can use the&nbsp;<a href=3D"/display/USER/Schedule+Block">Schedule B=
lock</a> to select Content items and plan the times at which they will be d=
isplayed on a Landing Page.</p>
</div>
</div>
